      <h2 class="h2">It Takes a City (Cambridge)</h2>
      <div class="quote">
        <p class="quote__body text-center">It Takes a City (Cambridge) is a new charitable company set up to support, facilitate and coordinate the Action Groups, communicate and liaise on behalf of the partnership, and raise the funds needed to deliver the solutions.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
